## RAG need : 
1.Outdated Knowledge : each llm has certain knowledge cutoff date , its not able to consume knowledge after that cutoff date .
2.Privacy : (question on personal finacial data , or compony finacia data ..that llm not seen during his training)- llm will not able to answer on this questions 
with RAG we can connect our private documents with it.
3.Hallucinations : in simple words its phenomenon where llm provides false info 
e.g: give me best ai papers of 2026 ? (it gave 10 links out of which 5 throws 404 error which means it doesnt exists)
-with RAG we can ground LLm that answer only using information given to you.

# RAG works on principle of IN Context Learning 
# LLM has parametric Knowledge (it learned during training)